Nd5 4. c4 Nc7 5. b4 d6 6. exd6 Qxd6 7. Nf3 {Relatively unexplored territory.}
Nc6) (2... d6 3. b4 Nf6 4. Nc3 Nc6 5. bxc5 dxc5 6. Bc4 {I like this structure
